  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Protection of Religious Heritage as a Tool for Reconciliation</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In cooperation with the Ministry of Culture, and in close consultation with the religious authorities &amp; civil society organizations representing minority groups, this project aims at providing protection to religious sites affected by Daesh/ISIL in Iraq&apos;s liberated areas, in such ways to promote the inter-community reconciliation through the protection of cultural diversity in Iraq. Establishment of the &quot;mapping and damage/needs assessment of the diverse religious heritage in Iraq&quot; will be distributed and published (printed &amp; online) to be used as a tool for comprehensive restoration.</narrative>
  </description>
